		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Ni&#1080;tendo did not disqualify games if sprites popped into view at the top of the screen. Play Super Mario Bros. 3 with an emulator set to show all 240 lines showing and then have Luigi approach the top of the screen (especially in world 3-9, where I first noticed it years ago).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


